Then for big screen: 
```css
@media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    .messageContent, .myMessageContent {
        max-width: 50vw;
    }
}
```
For small screen:
```css
@media screen and (max-width: 1000px) {
    .messageContent, .myMessageContent {
        max-width: 70vw;
